<div class="wrapper ">
  <div class="main-panel w-100">
    <div class="content">
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-header card-header-primary">
                <h4 class="card-title font-weight-light">Thông tin chi tiết</h4>
              </div>
              <div class="card-body">
                <form>
                  <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                      <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="bmd-label-floating">Tên đăng nhập</label>
                        <p style="font-weight:500;"><%=user.name%></p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                      <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="bmd-label-floating">Email</label>
                        <p style="font-weight:500;"><%=user.email%></p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                      <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="bmd-label-floating">Ngày sinh</label>
                        <!-- <p><%=user.birthday%></p> -->
                        <p style="font-weight:500;">12/04/1998</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                      <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="bmd-label-floating">Số điện thoại</label>
                        <p style="font-weight:500;"><%=user.phoneNumber%></p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-12">
                        <label>Giới thiệu</label>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="row">
                      <div class="col-md-12">
                          <p style="font-weight:500;">Tôi thích xem phim, đặc biệt là các thể loại hành động và kinh dị.
                             Bởi khi xem những phim đấy tôi cảm thấy mình trở nên mạnh mẽ hơn. 
                            </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row mt-5">
                        <div class="col-md-12 d-flex justify-content-center">
                          <a href="/users">
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Quay lại</button>
                          </a>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                  <div class="clearfix"></div>
                </form>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card card-profile">
              <div class="card-avatar">
                <a href="#pablo">
                  <img class="img" src="../assets/img/faces/marc.jpg" />
                </a>
              </div>
              <div class="card-body">
                <h6 class="card-category text-gray">CEO / Co-Founder</h6>
                <h4 class="card-title">Alec Thompson</h4>
                <p class="card-description h-100">
                  Don't be scared of the truth because we need to restart the
                  human foundation in truth And I love you like Kanye loves
                  Kanye I love Rick Owens’ bed design but the back is...
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
